# shadowColor

.Synopsis
Define the color of a [shadow].

.Syntax

.Types

.Function

*  `FProperty shadowColor(Color c)`
*  `FProperty shadowColor(str colorName)`

.Details

.Description
Defines the color of shadows. Also see <<shadow>> and <<shadowPos>>.

.Examples
[source,rascal-figure,width=,height=,file=s1.png]
----
                box1 = box(size(200,100), shadow(true), shadowColor("green"), resizable(false));
render(box1);
----

